               <p>JAMES RAPLEY. I am a <rs id="t18270405-235-viclabel1290" type="occupation">carrier</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18270405-235-victim1312 t18270405-235-viclabel1290"></join>, and live at Edmonton. On the 5th of March I received a box from Mr. Johnson of Charterhouse-lane - I left my cart in <placeName id="t18270405-235-crimeloc1291">Bread-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18270405-235-crimeloc1291" type="placeName" value="Bread-street"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18270405-235-crimeloc1291" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18270405-235-off1288 t18270405-235-crimeloc1291"></join> for four minutes, about half-past three o'clock; when I returned this box was gone - it is directed to Mr. Cox, Lower Edmonton.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18270405-235-person1313">
                  CHARLES 
                  HERDSFIELD
               <interp inst="t18270405-235-person1313" type="surname" value="HERDSFIELD"></interp>
