                     <interp inst="t18270405-235-person1313" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was coming up Foster-lane on the 5th of March, between three and four o'clock, and saw Dodson with this box and a bundle on his shoulder; Pretty, who was a few yards down the lane, then took the box - I seized him and called Stop thief! after Dodson, who was secured.</p>
               <p>
            
